      <p class="ml-5"> The app was coded with the Ruby on Rails Framework <br>
        but as the project progressed we were using a lot of AJAX <br>
        and Stimulus because everything had to be reactive. <br>
        I think the use of a javascript framework such as React <br>
        or Vue would have been a wise choice. It's very important<br>
        to choose the technical stack according to the project<br>
        specifications.
